        {
            "title": "A股半日近高位收市   深股重上15000關",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股半日收升，開市已為半日低位，近最高位收市，深股重上15000關，兩市成交合計16209.19億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_ASHARE_5_source-ap_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_ASHARE_5_source-ap_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指半日收報4094，升16點或0.4%，今早以4061點開市，跌16點或0.41%，已為半日低位，隨即節節向上，最高報4096，升18點或0.44%，半日成交7062.08億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指半日報15064點，升233點或1.58%，今早開市報14751點，亦跌79點或0.53%，亦為半日低位，最高報15076，升246點或1.65%，半日成交9147.11億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數半日報4788，升30點或0.64%，今早開跌20點或0.43%，開報4737點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數半日收報3678，升81點或2.27%，今早開市報3578點，跌18點或0.51%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15936869-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e8%bf%91%e9%ab%98%e4%bd%8d%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e9%87%8d%e4%b8%8a15000%e9%97%9c",
